# ENGINEERING DEVELOPMENT GUIDE

**Project:** JanPrashna Portal

**Version:** 1.0

---

# 1. Purpose

This document defines the engineering standards, coding conventions, architecture rules, and AI development workflow for JanPrashna Portal.

Every contributor (human or AI) must follow this guide.

---

# 2. Development Principles

* Follow the existing architecture.
* Never rewrite completed modules unnecessarily.
* Build reusable components.
* Keep business logic out of UI components.
* Prefer composition over duplication.
* Maintain accessibility (WCAG AA).
* Optimize for readability and maintainability.

---

# 3. Project Structure

Monorepo

apps/

* citizen-portal
* admin-dashboard
* backend-api

packages/

* ui
* types
* utils
* validators
* constants
* hooks
* ai

