# 5. Coding Standards

## TypeScript

* Strict Mode enabled
* No `any`
* Prefer interfaces for shared models
* Export types from shared packages

## Python

* Type hints required
* PEP 8 compliant
* Separate routers, services, repositories, and schemas
* Business logic must not live in API routes

